** 聯邦選舉：基於[[加拿大選舉法|加拿大選舉法]](''Canada Elections Act'')的修訂；
** 非聯邦選舉：
*** [[魁北克|魁北克]]：1963年<ref name="Canada">[http://www.elections.ca/eca/eim/article_search/article.asp?id=53&lang=e&frmPageSize=&textonly=false Elections Canada On-Line] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070922161833/http://www.elections.ca/eca/eim/article_search/article.asp?id=53&lang=e&frmpagesize=&textonly=false |date=2007-09-22 }}</ref>
