* [[德國|德國]]：1970年<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20000531154601/http://www.geocities.com/capitolhill/lobby/8522/wahl16_e.html</ref>
* [[荷蘭|荷蘭]]：1971年
* [[美國|美國]]：1971年7月1日 ([[Twenty-sixth_Amendment_to_the_United_States_Constitution|XXVI Amendment to the Constitution]], [[Alaska|Alaska]] from 19, [[Hawaii|Hawaii]] and [[New_Hampshire|New Hampshire]] from 20; federal voting age previously reduced on 1971-01-01 by the [[Voting_Rights_Act#Periodic_Renewal|Voting Rights Act Amendments 1970]], ss. 302, 305<ref>Title 3, 84 Stat. 318, 42 U.S.C. Sec. 1973bb.; text reproduced in [[Oregon_v._Mitchell|Oregon v. Mitchell]], 400 U.S. 112, 223</ref>)
:prior reductions: [[Georgia_(U.S._state)|Georgia]] in August 1943<ref>{{cite news|title=Suffrage Jr.|publisher=Time|date=1943-08-16|accessdate=2007-02-05}}</ref> and [[Kentucky|Kentucky]] in 1955;<ref name="Maryland"/> [[Guam|Guam]] in 1954<ref name="Cheng">{{cite news
